'''哈爾科夫河'''是[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的河流，位於[[卡爾可夫州|卡爾可夫州]]，屬於[[洛潘河|洛潘河]]的左支流<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.encyclopediaofukraine.com/display.asp?linkpath=pages%5CK%5CH%5CKharkivoblast.htm|title = Kharkiv Oblast|date = |accessdate = 12 July 2015|website = Internet [[Encyclopedia_of_Ukraine|Encyclopedia of Ukraine]]|publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2022-02-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220227145057/http://www.encyclopediaofukraine.com/display.asp?linkpath=pages%5CK%5CH%5CKharkivoblast.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref>，發源自[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[別爾哥羅德州|別爾哥羅德州]]，河道全長71公里，[[流域|流域]]面積1,160平方公里。

哈爾科夫河以所在城市[[哈爾科夫|哈爾科夫]]來命名<ref>{{Cite book|title = Historical Dictionary of Ukraine|last = Katchanovski|first = Ivan|publisher = Scarecrow Press, Inc.|year = 2013|isbn = 9780810878471|location = Lanham, Maryland|pages = 253|last2 = Kohut|first2 = Zenon E.|last3 = Nebesio|first3 = Bohdan Y.|last4 = Yurkevich|first4 = Myroslav}}</ref>。

